Professor Coleman is hands down my favourite Professor at UTM. One of the only classes I was actually learned from. Do the readings before his classes and you will be successful. Such a sweetheart, very approachable and extremely fair marker.   All the best, Sheri

Coleman made this subject exciting, when I dreaded having to take the class at first. READ. The classes are better because he expects discussion, this is the only way to dive into the topic and understand it. It's easy if you take the class seriously-and NO TESTS! Awesome.
Very engaging and knowledgeable about the subject, exactly what makes an epic professor!
If you want a professor who is truly passionate about the subject, and someone who will really teach you stuff then 1010 would recommend

He is really understanding and he cares a lot about his students. Reading the materials will get you far since the class is all about engagement & discussion. Make sure to take his 400-level course! He's the best prof, in my opinion.

Coleman works constantly towards making material easy to understand while nurturing the abilities of students. He sees the best in students and believes everyone can do their best. If you honestly try he will recognize and reward you. Doesn't make it hard to do very well. Not enough people realize they should take his Latin American courses.
Favourite Professor! He is understanding and really seeks the best interest of his students.
